text: Maria "Magalì" Vettorazzo (16 March 1942 – 18 June 2018) was an Italian female pentathlete. She competed at the 1968 Summer Olympics and finished in 21st place. Vettorazzo was born in Preganziol, Italy.Magali Vettorazzo . sports- reference.com Vettorazzo died on 18 June 2018 at the age of 76. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:1942 births Category:2018 deaths Category:Olympians for Italy
